title: Madonna Sticky & Sweet Buenos Aires Argentina SKY 1
description:
This is my recording of Madonna Sticky & Sweet Tour Buenos Aires Argentina off UK Sky 1 broadcast on 4th July 2009.  This is in HQ pro shot Mpeg 2 wide screen PAL 720x576.  I have edited out all the adverts in the breaks.  I didnt make it into a dvd as i couldnt be bothered lol, and no doubt this will have a commercial official DVD release soon anyways.  And all DVD players play mpeg 2 so i'm sure we can live without the chapters for now.

Enjoy

StephenUK :)
